          </div>
          <h3 class="text-xl font-semibold text-gray-900 mb-6" data-text="services-capabilities">Technical Capabilities</h3>
          <ul class="space-y-3 text-gray-600">
            <li class="flex items-start">
              <span class="w-1.5 h-1.5 bg-gray-400 rounded-full mt-2 mr-3 flex-shrink-0"></span>
              Advanced mechanical design (SolidWorks)
            </li>
            <li class="flex items-start">
              <span class="w-1.5 h-1.5 bg-gray-400 rounded-full mt-2 mr-3 flex-shrink-0"></span>
              Electrical systems design (E-plan)
            </li>
